#
# Random Weapons
#
# By Al Pence
#
#References tables shipped with TS:
#	Gems.tab
#	Magic Weapon Names.tab
#	Materials.tab
#	Creatures.tab
#		(Note: Creatures.tab is missing the Dragons group, causing an error.  I just went in and
#		 created a quick and dirty one right in the table file.  Or you can comment out the
#		 group call in Materials.tab.  Also there is a call made to Humanoid.tab in Materials.tab,
#		 that doesn't appear to exist.  I just commented it out till I either make a .tab file, or
#		 locate the missing one.)
#
	
