:BuildSword
1-75,A [~Sword] forged of [~Common Metal], the grip crafted of [~Grip], [~DecorationType].<br>
_It is [~Age], and in [~Condition] condition.
76-95,A [~Sword] forged of [~Rare Metal], the grip crafted of [~Grip], [~DecorationType].<br>
_It is [~Age], and in [~Condition] condition.
96-100,A [~Sword] forged of [~Rare Metal], the grip crafted of [~Grip], [~DecorationType].<br>
_It is [~Age], and in [~Condition] condition.<br>
_This blade bears the name, [~Magic Weapon Names.Start], and is enchanted [Enchantment].

